Q. Where u stored metrics of Prometheus like in tsdb but how to assign storage to metrics we will create separate pod or pv pvc ?
Q We need to install Prometheus on all servers ? --> 
ЁЯФ╣ 1. Prometheus Server (Central)

Install Prometheus only once (or maybe 2тАУ3 instances for HA).

It pulls metrics (via HTTP) from your nodes, apps, or exporters.

ЁЯФ╣ 2. Exporters (per-node or per-service)

You install exporters like:

Node Exporter тЖТ on every Linux server (for CPU, memory, disk, etc.)

Blackbox Exporter тЖТ for probing endpoints (ping, HTTP)

Application Exporters тЖТ like MySQL exporter, Redis exporter, etc.

Prometheus connects to these exporters to scrape metrics.

